defaultICOM is the trade association, representing the Industrial and Commercial sectors of the Heating Industry and is made up from members who produce/market products used in that sector of the industry.  The majority of members are industr
defaultial and commercial boiler manufacturers, producing products which operate, in the main, on gas, oil and biomass fuels, although other fuels are used in specialist applications. ICOM also has the majority of packaged burner manufacturers as members, produci
defaultng burners to work with the industrial and commercial boilers and operating on gas, oil and bio-fuels.
defaultThe equipment is used for the production of hot water and steam to be used in heating systems and for process installations.
