defaultHeat Demanddefault&#xa0;default1.1default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultWhereas in the domestic sector, there is a similarity of use and output from one property to another, in the industrial/commercial sector this is not the case.  There are a considerable number of different heat demands from simple heating of a small office
default to the heating of a large manufacturing complex. There are also process applications which can vary from supplying hot water for a factory process to high grade steam for an industrial process. 
