defaultConclusionsdefault5.1default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultICOM supports the Government in it’s aim to reduce energy use and GHG emissions.
default5.2default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultICOM promotes the balanced approach to achieving the targets on energy and GHG emission reduction by using high efficiency gas &amp; oil boilers to work in conjunction
default with renewable energy equipment and intelligent pumps and controls to give the most efficient system design.
default5.3default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe use of the RHI should be expanded to include hybrid systems of renewable and fossil fuels which will help in achieving the reduction of energy
default use.
